<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Beautysalons</title>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poiret+One|Lato:400,300,700,900&subset=latin,latin-ext' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poiret+One' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <script src="//maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js"></script>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </button>
        <a class="navbar-brand logo" href="/">MOJA<span>LEPOTA</span></a>
      </div>
      <div id="navbar" class="navbar-collapse collapse">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li><%= link_to "Saloni", salons_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Cene", prices_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Usluge", services_path %></li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
          <!-- admin menu will go here -->
          <li><%= link_to "Saloni", salons_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Cene", prices_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "Usluge", services_path %></li>
          <!-- admin menu will go here -->
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="navbar navbar-purple">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <aside class="col-md-3">
        <h3 class="lead">Usluge</h3>
        <div class="panel panel-default panel-services">
          <!--<div class="panel-heading">Usluge:</div>-->
          <div class="panel-body">
            <%= render 'prices/countservices', :@prices => Price.all %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="lead">Login</h3>
        <div class="panel panel-default panel-login">
          <!--<div class="panel-heading">Login</div>-->
          <div class="panel-body">
            <form role="form">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Enter email">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="pwd">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pwd" placeholder="Enter password">
              </div>
              <div class="checkbox">
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Remember me</label>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Submit</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
      <div class="col-md-9">
        <%= yield %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="navbar-inverse">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3 class="logo">MOJA<span>LEPOTA</span></h3>
          <p>Dobrodošli na poral mojalepota.com! Ovaj portal namenjen je svima onima koji žele da pronađu kozmetičku uslugu po svojoj meri!</p>
          <p>Besplatnom registracijom, dobijate mogućnost pretrage salona i usluga i po udaljenosti! Kao i mogućnost praćenja salona i njihovih ponuda. Kao što smo rekli, registracija je potpuno besplatna.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Budite u toku!</h3>
            <p>Registrujte svoju email adresu koristeći kontakt formu, i budite uvek u toku sa najnovijim ponudama!</p>
          <form role="form">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Unesite ovde Vašu email adrese">
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">PRIJAVA</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Izdvajamo iz ponude</h3>
          <p>INSERT SALONS HERE LATER</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <h3>Kontakt</h3>
          <table class="table contact">
            <tr><td><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></span>Adresa:</td><td> Karađorđeva 6/153<br>11080, Beograd, Srbija</td></tr>
            <tr><td><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></span>Email:</td><td> office@mojalepota.com</td></tr>
            <tr><td><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone"></span>Telefon:</td><td> +381 (60) 6629 - 098</td></tr>
            <tr><td><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-headphones"></span>Podrška:</td><td> +381 (60) 6629 - 098<br>podrska@mojalepota.com</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
  <div class="copyright">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 text-left">
          Developed by PIXEL2GO.COM
        </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 text-right">
            2015 &copy; All rights recieved.
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
